    @DefaultSeverity(value=WARNING)
public abstract class SemanticWarningProblem
extends AbstractSemanticProblem
    Abstract superclass of all semantic warnings. It is termed a "problem" because the fact that it is in the problems package can be confusing unless Problem is ritually appended to its class name.
